{"tid":681974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[重腳味]大媽 歎冷氣　瞓鞋舖沙發好梳乎","createTime":"2018-05-28T13:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-28T14:09:54.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bbff5443142607c55e06910a63366c16dcdc0aa7","tid":681974,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T13:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180528/photo/bkn-20180528144813863-0528_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180528145106\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180528%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180528144813863-0528_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180528145106&h=0e3c51cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相片於周日（27日）被上載至社交群組「巴打絲打 Facebook Club」，發貼者表示，在旺角一間連鎖運動用品店內，有大媽疑睡在供人試鞋的梳化上。<br />\n<br />\n從相片可見，該大媽卸下粉紅色的背囊後，<span style=\"color: red;\">脫下鞋子</span>，如「臥佛」般側躺在梳化中間。有數名大媽坐在她旁邊，其中一人正側頭看着她。<br />\n<br />\n相片惹來網民熱議，有人諷謂︰「張床夠大夠闊，正呀，仲有免費冷氣，不得了。」有網民則「憂慮」大媽的健康，「佢暈咗呀，快啲叫白車。」不少人嘆道，近年在各大商場，均看過類似情況，直言「影響市容，不知所謂」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180528/bkn-20180528144813863-0528_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180528%2Fbkn-20180528144813863-0528_00822_001.html&d=sk7klDwSKyoYbvO4rZfjIQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=623f6b53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180528/bkn-20180528144813863-0528_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"2639c4e0df85a8faecadc3a0453dcec7716cd2fd","tid":681974,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T13:10:22.000Z","msg":"正仆街黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b8667d17d5cd1cce7078c789208e3afed837f0","tid":681974,"uid":184900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T13:12:35.000Z","msg":"隔住個mon都聞到"},{"pid":"1800cc8d8701a54007ae5e88775c3926a3b434ab","tid":681974,"uid":131084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-2